TASK- How to check the list of added user in the group.
SOLUTION- We can check the list of added users in a group by many commands -->
METHOD 1- By using /etc/group file:
          Use the grep command as follows:
          $ grep 'grpup-name-here' /etc/group
          $ grep 'ftponly' /etc/group
          $ grep -i --color 'ftponly' /etc/group 
METHOS 2- By using members command:
          $ members ftponly
